{"tid":1983031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《599C檢疫令》5月7日失效，限聚封舖延長指令同日结束，中國人全面入關消費","createTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T07:23:28.000Z","uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5376bd306d75a6259dcd20f068286a21aff9678b","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"第599C章 《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599C?xpid=ID_1581054140667_062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap599C%3Fxpid%3DID_1581054140667_062&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=2a9868c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599C?xpid=ID_1581054140667_062</a><br />\n<blockquote>3.對若干到港人士實行強制檢疫<br />\n(1)獲授權人員須藉書面命令，對到達香港並符合以下說明的人，實行檢疫，檢疫期為到港當日起計的14日 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(a)該人從內地、澳門或台灣到達香港；或</span><br />\n(b)該人在到港當日之前的14日期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾在內地、澳門或台灣逗留任何時間。</span> (2020年第28號法律公告)</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>12.失效日期<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>本規例在2020年5月7日午夜失效。</ins></strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n《預防及控制疾病（規定及指示）（業務及處所）規例》及《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》最新指示<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/21/P2020042100184.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F21%2FP2020042100184.htm&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b4012b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/21/P2020042100184.htm</a><br />\n<blockquote>食物及衞生局局長今日（四月二十一日）根據第599F章及第599G章藉在憲報刊登的公告發出最新指示：<br />\n（一）撤銷要求餐飲處所內的顧客數目，在任何時間均不得超過該處所通常座位數目的50%；<br />\n（二）延長所有其他就餐飲業務、表列處所及禁止羣組聚集已實施的要求十四天，由二○二○年四月二十四日凌晨零時起<span style=\"color: red;\">生效至二○二○年五月七日。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2nnkmdr/ctp-vzntr/EWAHt9r19snyAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2nnkmdr%2Fctp-vzntr%2FEWAHt9r19snyAB.jpg&h=ee9940a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清兵蝗蟲全面入關人民幣消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dbfc74c4c6f033217699cd97602419c77d9e27","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"立法會議員郭家麒醫生擔心，政府突然徵用九龍城區的酒店作候檢中心，有可能是特區政府為重開高鐵西九龍站及放寬內地人來港檢疫限制的先兆，因富豪東方酒店位於九龍城，與高鐵西九龍站相距不遠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1146083b604ff5dec2c5365d2ee8859c51594646","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"第599D章 《預防及控制疾病(披露資料)規例》<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年5月7日午夜失效</span><br />\n<br />\n第599E章 《外國地區到港人士強制檢疫規例》<br />\n2020年6月18日午夜失效<br />\n<br />\n第599F章 《預防及控制疾病(規定及指示)(業務及處所)規例》<br />\n2020年6月28日午夜失效<br />\n<br />\n第599G章 《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》<br />\n2020年6月28日午夜失效"},{"pid":"0ac5b27c0abc713ef7e5bde8c4609b679d6e8fee","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"3月16日起已沒有再作更新俗稱「599C」的《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》強制檢疫人士所居住的大廈名單。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1950255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1950255</a>"},{"pid":"b3525411a6f75bc03c7bd107ec679330629e81a1","tid":1983031,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f30d7e7b0534f41a81788a8be19108c560225243","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3525411a6f75bc03c7bd107ec679330629e81a1","tid":1983031,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"入嚟時事台睇吓反應如何"},{"pid":"76351a9c16e7c1474068acfa26d8fd55f1103822","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:18