e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/599c_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F599c_tc.pdf&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=c7b01da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/599c_tc.pdf</a><br />\n599C名單自從16號之後就再冇更新過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n而家係3月26號?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:14:21.000Z","msg":"要減返14日架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14 15當佢六日放假啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca373392432169c7071af0ed6d661db519545623","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"2020-03-31 HKT 11:03<br />\n <br />\n林鄭月娥在行政會議前說，內地近日確診個案大多數是輸入病例，但現階段不會放寬相關入境限制及重開來往內地的關口。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，疫情不穩定仍有變數，加上收緊入境限制後，經港珠澳大橋及深圳灣入境人士數目顯著下跌，因此沒有很大需要重開關口。另外，根據《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章），當局會對所有內地抵港者發出檢疫令，強制有關人士必須實行家居檢疫14天；<span style=\"color: red;\">但此規定有時限，到5月初便會失效，屆時也會自動恢復部分交通流。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fa9fd68c95765934eaa40824fd8b7b71cbfda7","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76351a9c16e7c1474068acfa26d8fd55f1103822","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"今日冇人問777會唔會延長599C都幾神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/14/P2020041400715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F14%2FP2020041400715.htm&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=85e290a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/14/P2020041400715.htm</a><br />\n2020年4月14日<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>記者：其實很多市民都關注五月七日便是內地抵港人士強制檢疫令失效，其實政府會否考慮延長這個措施？謝謝。<br />\n <br />\n777：但距離你剛才提及第599C章規定內地入境人士14日強制檢疫的失效日期還有三個多星期，所以我們都要密切留意情況。<span style=\"color: red;\">當然有需要的時候是可以延長的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再返回行政會議商討是可以延長的</span>，但我今日真的說不定，因為疫情的變化是可能很快。我們那麼辛苦接近三個月的抗疫，能夠走到這一步，沒有大型的社區爆發，是不應該因為爭朝夕而令我們前功盡廢。</blockquote>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"31455bafdb966e3ba23f70e1f2d0dc62b87ed787","tid":1983031,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母 真係冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}